Title : Church of the Archangels Michael and Gabriel, Șurdești
Text : [[File:Surdesti-0269-a.jpg|thumb|Șurdești wooden church]]
The '''Church of the Archangels Michael and Gabriel''' is a [[Romanian Church United with Rome, Greek-Catholic|Greek-Catholic]] church in Șurdești village, [[Șișești, Maramureș|Șișești]] Commune, [[Maramureș County]], [[Romania]]. Built in 1721, it is one of eight buildings that make up the [[wooden churches of Maramureș]] [[UNESCO World Heritage Site]],<ref>[http://whc.unesco.org/en/list/904 Wooden Churches of Maramureș] at the UNESCO site</ref> and is also listed as a [[Monument istoric|historic monument]] by the country's [[Ministry of Culture and Religious Affairs (Romania)|Ministry of Culture and Religious Affairs]].<ref>{{ro icon}} [http://www.patrimoniu.ro/images/LMI/LMI-2010_MM.pdf Lista Monumentelor Istorice 2010: Judeţul Maramureş]{{Dead link|date=July 2019 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}, p.1728</ref>

